        <abstract>
            <p>A. J. Gaudry is one of few supporters of Darwinism in Paris.</p>
            <p>The climate is so hostile that Kovalevsky must mitigate his views so as not to irritate the French.</p> 
<p>Working on <hi rend="italic">Anchitherium</hi>, which he believes is intermediate between <hi rend="italic">Palaeotherium</hi> and the horse.</p> 
            <p>His brother-in-law has been arrested.</p>
        </abstract>
